        "text_HmPAx9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p> Environmental Biotech is proud to announce that many of our<br/>products have earned EPA Safer Choice certification. The EPA’s Safer Choice program “helps consumers, businesses, and purchasers find products that perform effectively while using ingredients that are safer for human health and the environment.”</p><p>It is important to note that the EPA Safer Choice label does<br/>not constitute an endorsement of the product. Instead, it signifies that the formula, as represented to the EPA by Environmental Biotech, includes ingredients with better health and environmental profiles compared to conventional products of a similar type. The EPA relies on Environmental Biotech’s integrity and transparency regarding product composition, ingredients, and attributes. While the EPA has not independently analyzed the ingredients nor verified any non-ingredient claims, it provides this certification based on the product’s health and environmental characteristics as outlined in the Safer Choice Standard and current scientific understanding.</p>",
